WEBVTT

1
04:59:59.000 --> 08:06:59.000
Subtitles downloaded from www.OpenSubtitles.org

2
00:02:49.163 --> 00:02:51.131
Good luck. General Yin.

3
00:02:57.371 --> 00:02:59.931
A man must do or die.

4
00:02:59.974 --> 00:03:02.909
Mr. Ho. before I left.

5
00:03:02.943 --> 00:03:04.308
Lord Cheng is concerned about you.

6
00:03:04.345 --> 00:03:07.109
If he can strike back with his army.

7
00:03:07.147 --> 00:03:09.479
And defeat the tartars.

8
00:03:09.516 --> 00:03:13.885
Credit for Canton will be yours.

9
00:03:13.921 --> 00:03:18.255
One must sacrifice for one's country.

10
00:03:18.292 --> 00:03:21.955
The brothers arrested by tartars...

11
00:03:21.996 --> 00:03:26.160
Were tortured but have so far...

12
00:03:26.200 --> 00:03:28.191
Refused to make a confession.

13
00:03:28.235 --> 00:03:30.066
This is most admirable.

14
00:03:32.339 --> 00:03:33.431
If I fail...

15
00:03:33.474 --> 00:03:35.635
I wouldn't even get arrested.

16
00:03:35.676 --> 00:03:36.904
General Yin.

17
00:03:36.944 --> 00:03:39.378
Mr. Ho. please.

18
00:03:39.880 --> 00:03:42.075
North Door

19
00:04:12.513 --> 00:04:13.878
Sirs.

20
00:04:13.914 --> 00:04:19.079
When inspector-gen.
And Gen. Tien Ta...

21
00:04:19.119 --> 00:04:25.080
arrive. please say a good word for me.

22
00:04:25.125 --> 00:04:28.959
Don't worry. Mr. Magistrate.

23
00:04:28.996 --> 00:04:32.159
General Tien Ta ordered us.

24
00:04:32.199 --> 00:04:34.463
To capture the traitors.

25
00:04:34.501 --> 00:04:37.698
The inspector

26
00:04:37.738 --> 00:04:41.538
Will supervise the execution.

27
00:04:41.575 --> 00:04:42.837
Yes. yes...

28
00:04:42.876 --> 00:04:46.209
Tang San-yao. it's almost 12:30.

29
00:04:46.246 --> 00:04:49.272
- Don't forget the General's command.
- Yes.

30
00:04:49.316 --> 00:04:53.616
The inspector-general is here.

31
00:04:53.654 --> 00:04:54.643
Make way...

32
00:04:54.688 --> 00:04:57.384
Make way...

33
00:05:53.213 --> 00:05:54.510
We're trapped!

34
00:05:56.016 --> 00:05:59.850
General Yin. I knew you'd be here.

35
00:05:59.887 --> 00:06:01.514
To "welcome" the inspector-general.

36
00:06:06.894 --> 00:06:11.058
But he has not yet reached Canton!

37
00:06:31.185 --> 00:06:32.709
Stop.

38
00:06:34.955 --> 00:06:36.980
Your skill is comparable to a general.

39
00:06:37.024 --> 00:06:40.289
Let's have a fair fight:

40
00:06:40.327 --> 00:06:43.194
A General to a General.

41
00:06:43.230 --> 00:06:46.893
Let me try you out.

42
00:06:46.934 --> 00:06:51.371
Good. I need a substitute.

43
00:08:00.674 --> 00:08:03.234
Let me fight you single-handedly.

44
00:08:48.021 --> 00:08:50.182
Quiet down.

45
00:08:50.223 --> 00:08:51.918
The teacher's here.

46
00:08:51.959 --> 00:08:55.656
The teacher's here. hurry up...

47
00:08:59.232 --> 00:09:00.631
Mr. Ho.

48
00:09:05.038 --> 00:09:06.198
Mr. Ho.

49
00:09:26.893 --> 00:09:32.593
What's it?
What's happened to Mr. Ho?

50
00:09:35.035 --> 00:09:36.559
Mr. Ho.

51
00:09:49.983 --> 00:09:51.280
Please have some tea. Mr. Ho.

52
00:09:59.993 --> 00:10:03.019
Mr. Ho. why are you so late?

53
00:10:03.063 --> 00:10:04.530
Did you watch the execution?

54
00:10:06.566 --> 00:10:07.624
Leave me alone!

55
00:10:07.668 --> 00:10:10.136
Isn't it enjoyable to watch executions?

56
00:10:10.170 --> 00:10:15.107
Lin Zhen. it depends on who it is.

57
00:10:15.142 --> 00:10:19.306
If it is the tartars who invaded us...

58
00:10:19.346 --> 00:10:20.904
Of course it is gratifying.

59
00:10:20.947 --> 00:10:27.443
But today's convicts are patriots.

60
00:10:27.487 --> 00:10:30.547
They are all Han's martyrs.

61
00:10:30.590 --> 00:10:32.922
Do you still think it is enjoyable?

62
00:10:32.959 --> 00:10:35.052
I...

63
00:10:36.997 --> 00:10:40.524
Yesterday. I taught you sacrifice.

64
00:10:40.567 --> 00:10:43.058
For the sake of a righteous cause.

65
00:10:43.103 --> 00:10:47.403
Do you all understand?

66
00:10:47.441 --> 00:10:49.033
Yes.

67
00:10:52.012 --> 00:10:53.673
Hurry up...

68
00:10:58.952 --> 00:11:00.112
It's here.

69
00:11:17.204 --> 00:11:18.899
Is he dead or alive?

70
00:11:18.939 --> 00:11:22.932
He's so stiff. of course he's dead.

71
00:11:26.713 --> 00:11:28.738
He's a hero.

72
00:11:31.151 --> 00:11:32.243
What did you say?

73
00:11:32.285 --> 00:11:34.048
I...

74
00:11:34.087 --> 00:11:35.418
- Arrest him.
- Yes.

75
00:11:35.455 --> 00:11:38.049
You're an accomplice.

76
00:11:38.091 --> 00:11:41.925
Lord Tang... Listen to me.

77
00:11:41.962 --> 00:11:44.226
This student is not a bad man.

78
00:11:44.264 --> 00:11:46.926
He's the son of a seafood shop owner.

79
00:11:46.967 --> 00:11:52.667
- Son of a shop owner?
- Yes. exactly.

80
00:11:52.706 --> 00:11:56.164
These are his classmates.

81
00:11:56.209 --> 00:11:58.109
Yes. we're his classmates.

82
00:11:58.145 --> 00:11:59.942
Where are you studying?

83
00:11:59.980 --> 00:12:04.940
They all study in Chong Wen College.

84
00:12:04.985 --> 00:12:08.887
Are you vouching for them. Mr. Wang?

85
00:12:08.922 --> 00:12:13.120
Yes. Apologize to Lord Tang.

86
00:12:13.160 --> 00:12:15.560
I...

87
00:12:15.595 --> 00:12:17.324
You're young and ignorant.

88
00:12:17.364 --> 00:12:18.353
Always causing trouble.

89
00:12:23.470 --> 00:12:26.667
Do you know who I am?

90
00:12:26.706 --> 00:12:30.733
I do. Tang San-yao. Lord Tang.

91
00:12:35.115 --> 00:12:36.548
Yes. let's go. quickly!

92
00:12:39.553 --> 00:12:41.418
Uncle Wang.
we didn't do anything wrong.

93
00:12:41.454 --> 00:12:44.855
Yes. I know.
Tang San-yao's notorious…

94
00:12:44.891 --> 00:12:47.223
for his craze after money and women.

95
00:12:47.260 --> 00:12:50.923
You mustn't antagonize him.

96
00:12:50.964 --> 00:12:55.594
As the saying goes. "One must..."

97
00:12:55.635 --> 00:12:57.535
humble oneself under enemy's rule."

98
00:13:08.615 --> 00:13:14.019
Mr. Ho... please open the door!

99
00:13:14.054 --> 00:13:15.453
Who is it?

100
00:13:15.488 --> 00:13:16.648
Mr. Ho.

101
00:13:20.260 --> 00:13:21.454
Open the door. Mr. Ho.

102
00:13:21.494 --> 00:13:22.518
Mr. Ho.

103
00:13:28.134 --> 00:13:29.328
Mr. Ho! …

104
00:13:32.205 --> 00:13:34.901
What's wrong?

105
00:13:34.941 --> 00:13:35.965
I...

106
00:13:36.009 --> 00:13:38.569
There's something we don't understand.

107
00:13:38.612 --> 00:13:40.842
So we've come here even at this hour.

108
00:13:40.881 --> 00:13:44.214
Humble oneself under enemy's rule.

109
00:13:44.251 --> 00:13:46.412
Do we and our children have to...

110
00:13:46.453 --> 00:13:49.081
Humble ourselves forever?

111
00:13:54.294 --> 00:13:56.626
I'd say. we'd be beheaded if we didn't.

112
00:13:56.663 --> 00:13:59.188
If we fear not death we don't have to.

113
00:13:59.232 --> 00:14:02.565
You're right. It's well said.

114
00:14:02.602 --> 00:14:07.039
One brave man alone is not enough.

115
00:14:07.073 --> 00:14:11.066
But unity is strength.

116
00:14:11.111 --> 00:14:14.137
The tartars are well-armed.

117
00:14:14.180 --> 00:14:15.340
We...

118
00:14:15.382 --> 00:14:19.876
Man owes allegiance to his country.

119
00:14:19.920 --> 00:14:24.983
Lord Cheng is recruiting in Taiwan.

120
00:14:25.025 --> 00:14:27.994
He's become tartar's biggest concern.

121
00:14:28.028 --> 00:14:31.486
The Manchurian emperor has ordered...

122
00:14:31.531 --> 00:14:33.431
Coastal residents to move away.

123
00:14:33.466 --> 00:14:37.232
And to be on their guard.

124
00:14:37.270 --> 00:14:38.635
Mr. Ho.

125
00:14:38.672 --> 00:14:40.936
I wish Lord Cheng could use us.

126
00:14:40.974 --> 00:14:42.999
The day will come.

127
00:14:43.043 --> 00:14:46.171
Don't you all want to help?

128
00:14:46.212 --> 00:14:47.907
Yes.

129
00:14:47.948 --> 00:14:51.076
- Good. Come here.
- Yes.

130
00:14:56.890 --> 00:15:00.656
Secret documents will arrive by sea.

131
00:15:00.694 --> 00:15:03.993
I need a way to bypass customs.

132
00:15:04.030 --> 00:15:05.895
Liu Yu-de

133
00:15:05.932 --> 00:15:08.400
- Doesn't your pa run a seafood shop?
- Yes.

134
00:15:21.614 --> 00:15:23.047
Open sesame...

135
00:15:23.083 --> 00:15:25.916
Shut sesame...

136
00:15:30.190 --> 00:15:31.987
Mr. Ho sent us here.

137
00:15:32.025 --> 00:15:33.253
Good.

138
00:15:39.899 --> 00:15:42.060
Little brother. you're a brave fellow.

139
00:15:50.343 --> 00:15:53.278
Lock it up...

140
00:15:53.313 --> 00:15:54.837
Yes. hurry...

141
00:15:54.881 --> 00:15:57.349
Pa. has San Li's abalone arrived?

142
00:15:57.384 --> 00:16:00.581
The abalone... Go. go now!

143
00:16:00.620 --> 00:16:02.178
It has... The sea cucumber has too...

144
00:16:16.369 --> 00:16:19.361
Te. what are you doing?

145
00:16:19.406 --> 00:16:22.307
A big order for abalone was placed.

146
00:16:22.342 --> 00:16:24.401
I am showing them some samples.

147
00:16:24.444 --> 00:16:29.006
So you're in business now?

148
00:16:33.486 --> 00:16:36.978
Te. you can't take the whole case.

149
00:16:37.023 --> 00:16:38.149
I'm in a hurry to deliver it.

150
00:16:38.191 --> 00:16:40.989
Hurry? Do you know
the market price?

151
00:16:41.027 --> 00:16:45.589
The quality's high.
Raise the price.

152
00:16:45.632 --> 00:16:47.031
Open it

153
00:16:47.067 --> 00:16:48.932
Yes.

154
00:16:55.175 --> 00:16:56.403
Excellent kung fu.

155
00:16:56.443 --> 00:17:00.504
You'll find that at Shaolin Temple.

156
00:17:03.583 --> 00:17:05.574
Mr. Ho. we could invite them to...

157
00:17:05.618 --> 00:17:06.915
Yes.

158
00:17:06.953 --> 00:17:13.017
They don't involve in worldly matters.

159
00:17:13.059 --> 00:17:16.460
If Shaolin taught kung fu to laymen.

160
00:17:16.496 --> 00:17:20.364
People could fight the tartars.

161
00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:21.594
That would be great!

162
00:17:39.552 --> 00:17:41.383
Yue Shan. South gate...

163
00:17:45.158 --> 00:17:46.716
Here.

164
00:17:46.993 --> 00:17:50.622
General Tien.

165
00:17:50.663 --> 00:17:52.426
Arise.

166
00:17:52.465 --> 00:17:54.524
Come over here.

167
00:18:01.241 --> 00:18:05.541
Lately. we've suppressed rebels.

168
00:18:05.578 --> 00:18:08.012
And found this on their leaders

169
00:18:08.047 --> 00:18:12.507
Zheng Cheng-gong's edict.

170
00:18:14.254 --> 00:18:15.414
Look. what have you been doing?

171
00:18:15.455 --> 00:18:19.551
There must be many of Cheng's men

172
00:18:19.592 --> 00:18:23.460
Hiding in Canton.

173
00:18:25.632 --> 00:18:30.899
We must capture the rebels.

174
00:18:30.937 --> 00:18:36.204
And kill them to scare them off…

175
00:18:58.264 --> 00:18:59.595
Who's that?

176
00:18:59.632 --> 00:19:04.365
No idea. He's secretive. maybe a spy.

177
00:19:04.404 --> 00:19:06.565
I'm innocent. I'm a delivery boy.

178
00:19:06.606 --> 00:19:08.073
I've brought dried fish. Look!

179
00:19:08.107 --> 00:19:09.904
Shut up.

180
00:19:31.965 --> 00:19:35.526
Lord Zheng. notorious rebels...

181
00:19:35.568 --> 00:19:39.527
Who told you to bring this here?

182
00:19:39.572 --> 00:19:43.702
No... no use to ask me.

183
00:19:48.414 --> 00:19:51.440
Kid. we'll take you away.

184
00:19:51.484 --> 00:19:59.484
And torture you one after another.

185
00:19:59.993 --> 00:20:02.928
And torture you one after another.

186
00:20:02.962 --> 00:20:04.486
See how long you will hold your silence.

187
00:20:07.000 --> 00:20:12.700
I'll talk... Don't torture me.

188
00:20:12.739 --> 00:20:18.507
I...I say.

189
00:20:22.048 --> 00:20:25.950
there is someone.

190
00:20:37.997 --> 00:20:45.062
Go on with the torture...

191
00:20:45.104 --> 00:20:47.436
if you like!

192
00:21:03.523 --> 00:21:06.492
I saw a squadron of Ching troops...

193
00:21:06.526 --> 00:21:08.994
Of over patrolling our alley.

194
00:21:09.028 --> 00:21:11.394
Mr. Ho. what shall we do?

195
00:21:11.431 --> 00:21:17.063
We must keep calm and
be on the alert.

196
00:21:17.103 --> 00:21:21.938
Yien-pin. let them hide in your home.

197
00:21:21.974 --> 00:21:24.340
Mr. Ho. what about you...

198
00:21:27.980 --> 00:21:29.038
Mr. Ho. Mr. Ho.

199
00:21:29.082 --> 00:21:30.481
- Go quickly. go!
- What about you?

200
00:21:30.516 --> 00:21:31.744
Hurry up. quick.

201
00:21:55.074 --> 00:21:56.939
Master. look!

202
00:21:56.976 --> 00:22:00.912
Please have mercy...
please talk to them.

203
00:22:00.947 --> 00:22:03.939
Please ask them not to...

204
00:22:03.983 --> 00:22:05.109
Quiet!

205
00:22:07.420 --> 00:22:10.617
General's order: No dried fish.

206
00:22:10.656 --> 00:22:12.521
Then...

207
00:22:12.558 --> 00:22:14.355
What's your relationship with Liu Yu-de.

208
00:22:14.394 --> 00:22:17.921
He... he's my son.

209
00:22:17.964 --> 00:22:19.295
Bring him here.

210
00:22:19.332 --> 00:22:23.701
He's not home...
What do you want him for?

211
00:22:23.736 --> 00:22:26.398
We've uncovered many spies recently.

212
00:22:26.439 --> 00:22:32.605
One's a teacher; another's his pupil.

213
00:22:35.047 --> 00:22:36.912
Liu Yu-de's a pupil of that school.

214
00:22:36.949 --> 00:22:39.884
We'll capture him and torture him!

215
00:22:39.919 --> 00:22:43.946
Master. our young master won't...

216
00:22:43.990 --> 00:22:45.355
Please have mercy.

217
00:22:45.391 --> 00:22:47.655
How do you know he wouldn't?

218
00:22:47.693 --> 00:22:49.991
Let's talk it over.

219
00:22:55.902 --> 00:22:56.960
Pa...

220
00:22:57.003 --> 00:22:59.062
Yu-de. run quickly... Yu-de

221
00:22:59.105 --> 00:23:01.573
Young Master. run. run quickly…

222
00:23:01.607 --> 00:23:04.405
Run quickly. Young Master.

223
00:23:04.444 --> 00:23:05.570
You want to rebel?

224
00:23:05.611 --> 00:23:09.547
Yu-de. run quickly. run!

225
00:23:36.409 --> 00:23:39.708
He's innocent! My son!

226
00:23:39.745 --> 00:23:42.213
Liu Yu-de. come up quickly.

227
00:23:42.248 --> 00:23:45.308
My son is innocent. my son!

228
00:23:56.929 --> 00:23:58.123
Change your clothes at once.

229
00:23:58.164 --> 00:23:59.495
I...

230
00:23:59.532 --> 00:24:01.397
All wearing school uniform will be
arrested.

231
00:24:01.434 --> 00:24:03.925
Wonder what's happened to my home?

232
00:24:03.970 --> 00:24:05.232
Try to find a hiding place first.

233
00:24:05.271 --> 00:24:07.000
We can find out later.

234
00:24:07.039 --> 00:24:08.370
Right. let's go now.

235
00:24:15.915 --> 00:24:17.041
What has happened to my home?

236
00:24:17.083 --> 00:24:19.643
Your home...

237
00:24:19.685 --> 00:24:21.482
Tell me...

238
00:24:21.521 --> 00:24:24.888
All the houses in the neighboring street...

239
00:24:24.924 --> 00:24:27.518
To your home have been cordoned off.

240
00:24:27.560 --> 00:24:29.050
What about my father?

241
00:24:50.583 --> 00:24:52.483
Pa...

242
00:24:52.518 --> 00:24:58.354
Don't be sad. It's the same for mine.

243
00:25:02.695 --> 00:25:04.253
I wish I had learnt kung fu.

244
00:25:04.297 --> 00:25:06.390
Instead of studying.

245
00:25:06.432 --> 00:25:10.892
So I could fight them.

246
00:25:10.937 --> 00:25:15.033
Studies teach us right from wrong.

247
00:25:15.074 --> 00:25:17.542
What's the use of that?

248
00:25:17.577 --> 00:25:20.137
We can't talk sense with the tartars.

249
00:25:27.486 --> 00:25:29.886
We can't stay in this town anymore.

250
00:25:29.922 --> 00:25:32.686
The martial arts headquarters is...

251
00:25:32.725 --> 00:25:34.386
Shaolin Temple.

252
00:25:40.967 --> 00:25:42.264
We're lucky we made it.

253
00:25:43.970 --> 00:25:45.267
Let's go straight on.

254
00:25:54.113 --> 00:25:57.139
Did you see a group of men riding by?

255
00:25:57.183 --> 00:26:01.381
Why don't you answer me?

256
00:26:01.420 --> 00:26:05.584
Let's go!

257
00:26:21.374 --> 00:26:22.500
Dismount and chase them.

258
00:26:22.541 --> 00:26:23.667
Yes.

259
00:26:23.709 --> 00:26:26.269
These two must be traitors.

260
00:26:26.312 --> 00:26:29.247
One watch the horses. others chase.

261
00:26:29.281 --> 00:26:30.441
Yes.

262
00:26:39.959 --> 00:26:41.119
Hurry up.

263
00:26:53.039 --> 00:26:54.233
Let's go.

264
00:27:14.894 --> 00:27:16.327
Liu Yu-de. mount it.

265
00:27:16.362 --> 00:27:17.852
Liu Yu-de?

266
00:27:17.897 --> 00:27:22.129
Liu Yu-de. escape now. Go!

267
00:27:22.168 --> 00:27:24.659
Don't let him get away.

268
00:27:39.719 --> 00:27:42.279
Liu Yu-de. good luck!

269
00:29:43.475 --> 00:29:46.535
Please give me some water.

270
00:30:10.302 --> 00:30:12.202
Thank you. uncle.

271
00:30:12.238 --> 00:30:16.538
How far is it to Shaolin Temple?

272
00:30:16.575 --> 00:30:20.136
It's not far. only up the mountain.

273
00:30:20.179 --> 00:30:24.309
But it looks like you wouldn't make it.

274
00:30:24.350 --> 00:30:28.514
I can... even if I have to crawl there!

275
00:30:33.525 --> 00:30:40.363
Sit down. I don't think you can.

276
00:30:43.235 --> 00:30:49.174
A few Shaolin monks buy
food here everyday.

277
00:30:49.208 --> 00:30:52.575
Their cart is over there.

278
00:31:02.454 --> 00:31:05.617
Hurry up...
Do it orderly and quickly.

279
00:31:08.694 --> 00:31:10.218
Get going. go!

280
00:31:10.262 --> 00:31:14.665
- Why is it so heavy?
- Yes. I don't know why.

281
00:31:14.700 --> 00:31:17.328
Go. You'll be punished if you're late.

282
00:31:17.369 --> 00:31:19.269
Let's go. quick!

283
00:31:22.041 --> 00:31:24.566
Push harder. harder. go!

284
00:31:39.425 --> 00:31:42.986
Hurry up. park the cart there.

285
00:31:43.028 --> 00:31:45.656
Come and lend a hand. everybody.

286
00:31:45.698 --> 00:31:48.531
Why are you standing there. come here.

287
00:31:48.567 --> 00:31:51.502
Take this to the kitchen. Be quick.

288
00:32:03.048 --> 00:32:04.447
Why are you so slow? Hurry up...

289
00:32:06.018 --> 00:32:08.282
- Hurry up.
- Yes.

290
00:32:23.202 --> 00:32:25.432
What's the matter?

291
00:32:25.471 --> 00:32:26.529
What's that man doing there?

292
00:32:30.976 --> 00:32:33.137
Stay calm. he can still be saved.

293
00:32:33.178 --> 00:32:35.271
Bring him inside. I'll tell the abbot.

294
00:33:45.918 --> 00:33:48.512
Sir. the abbot would like to see you.

295
00:33:48.554 --> 00:33:49.885
Thank you.

296
00:33:49.922 --> 00:33:52.652
This temple is not a sanctuary.

297
00:33:52.691 --> 00:33:54.659
You're spiteful and emotional.

298
00:33:54.693 --> 00:34:00.222
Unfit to stay in the temple.

299
00:34:00.265 --> 00:34:04.031
You're recovering. please leave soon.

300
00:34:10.375 --> 00:34:12.935
I had so much difficulty coming here.

301
00:34:12.978 --> 00:34:14.536
I won't leave.

302
00:34:14.580 --> 00:34:17.208
Don't be rude.

303
00:34:17.249 --> 00:34:24.087
Splendid. We believe in fate...

304
00:34:24.123 --> 00:34:28.321
And we believe fate has
brought you here.

305
00:34:28.360 --> 00:34:33.195
Brother. you mustn't make a precedence.

306
00:34:33.232 --> 00:34:39.068
He arrived here in a coma.

307
00:34:39.104 --> 00:34:41.368
But woke up after days.

308
00:34:41.406 --> 00:34:44.375
Perseverance to Buddhism.

309
00:34:44.409 --> 00:34:46.639
Warrants his admittance.

310
00:34:46.678 --> 00:34:51.308
Dharma also came to the east

311
00:34:51.350 --> 00:34:55.150
With such perseverance.

312
00:34:55.187 --> 00:35:00.591
And laid the foundation of Shaolin.

313
00:35:00.626 --> 00:35:07.930
What are your opinions. brothers?

314
00:35:07.966 --> 00:35:11.197
You're right. brother.

315
00:35:14.306 --> 00:35:15.603
Thank you abbot.

316
00:36:02.354 --> 00:36:03.378
Morning. sir.

317
00:36:07.893 --> 00:36:09.121
- Morning. sir.
- Morning.

318
00:36:11.697 --> 00:36:12.686
- Morning. sir.
- Morning.

319
00:36:23.942 --> 00:36:26.502
San Ta. San Ta.

320
00:36:26.545 --> 00:36:28.638
Morning. sir.

321
00:36:28.680 --> 00:36:33.242
How long have you been here?

322
00:36:33.285 --> 00:36:35.685
Over a year.

323
00:36:35.721 --> 00:36:39.213
Are you unable to endure destitution?

324
00:36:39.258 --> 00:36:42.489
No. not that. but...

325
00:36:44.896 --> 00:36:48.457
Don't hide anything from the Buddha.

326
00:36:48.500 --> 00:36:54.439
Before I came here. I heard

327
00:36:54.473 --> 00:36:56.134
Shaolin's the headquarters of kung fu.

328
00:36:56.174 --> 00:37:00.372
But for the past year.
I have only cleaned.

329
00:37:00.412 --> 00:37:02.903
I haven't seen any kung fu.

330
00:37:02.948 --> 00:37:06.645
You can learn kung fu if you want to.

331
00:37:06.685 --> 00:37:09.552
As long as they want to. any monk...

332
00:37:09.588 --> 00:37:13.490
Can learn from the chambers.

333
00:37:13.525 --> 00:37:17.552
If you don't tell us who would know?

334
00:37:17.596 --> 00:37:22.465
Why do you want to learn kung fu?

335
00:37:22.501 --> 00:37:24.901
Honestly. sir.

336
00:37:24.936 --> 00:37:28.394
Before I came here. I saw the people

337
00:37:28.440 --> 00:37:30.874
Oppressed by tyrannical rule.

338
00:37:30.909 --> 00:37:34.902
If they were able to learn kung fu.

339
00:37:34.946 --> 00:37:37.608
They could defend themselves.

340
00:37:37.649 --> 00:37:39.480
And combat enemies. Therefore...

341
00:37:41.520 --> 00:37:43.181
Good. good.

342
00:37:45.557 --> 00:37:47.457
San Ta.

343
00:37:47.492 --> 00:37:52.828
Buddhists shouldn't bear such thought.

344
00:37:52.864 --> 00:37:56.095
Don't mention it again!

345
00:37:56.134 --> 00:37:58.500
I won't abandon such a desire.

346
00:37:58.537 --> 00:38:01.836
Whatever the outcome.
I won't dare complain.

347
00:38:01.873 --> 00:38:04.364
Sir.

348
00:38:04.409 --> 00:38:08.368
Can I still learn kung fu?

349
00:38:08.413 --> 00:38:10.904
There're chambers in Shaolin.

350
00:38:10.949 --> 00:38:12.280
Which chamber do you want to
start with?

351
00:38:12.317 --> 00:38:16.913
Which is the most advanced?

352
00:38:16.955 --> 00:38:18.650
The top chamber. of course!

353
00:38:18.690 --> 00:38:20.920
Then I'll start from the top.

354
00:38:23.028 --> 00:38:24.120
Top Chamber

355
00:39:15.580 --> 00:39:17.138
Sir.

356
00:39:17.182 --> 00:39:18.547
Behold. the Buddha says.

357
00:39:18.583 --> 00:39:21.950
Emptiness is the Eternal Five.

358
00:39:21.987 --> 00:39:24.285
No sight. sound. smell. taste. sense.

359
00:39:25.290 --> 00:39:27.952
The five flavours dull the taste.

360
00:39:27.993 --> 00:39:33.522
The five tones deafen the ear.

361
00:39:33.565 --> 00:39:38.434
The five colours blind the eye.

362
00:39:38.470 --> 00:39:41.997
It can also not be seen.

363
00:39:42.040 --> 00:39:45.203
But it won't pass away.

364
00:39:45.243 --> 00:39:47.143
Being at one is eternal.

365
00:39:47.179 --> 00:39:52.981
But all things will come to you.

366
00:39:53.018 --> 00:39:56.317
Without wisdom... without...

367
00:39:56.354 --> 00:39:59.915
Leave!

368
00:39:59.958 --> 00:40:04.452
No wisdom. no gain.

369
00:40:04.496 --> 00:40:06.896
Gaining is not continuant.

370
00:40:06.932 --> 00:40:13.098
All men will come to me one?

371
00:40:13.138 --> 00:40:15.698
For there lies rest

372
00:40:15.740 --> 00:40:18.675
And happiness and peace

373
00:40:18.710 --> 00:40:20.644
It's invisible and inaudible

374
00:40:20.679 --> 00:40:22.670
And it's inexhaustible.

375
00:40:22.714 --> 00:40:24.944
Can you hear the sound of bells?

376
00:40:24.983 --> 00:40:30.649
The heart is calm. We hear nothing.

377
00:40:38.563 --> 00:40:43.000
How often do you recite the sutras?

378
00:40:43.034 --> 00:40:45.969
I...I...

379
00:40:46.004 --> 00:40:48.871
Go away!

380
00:40:48.907 --> 00:40:50.966
Sir. I came to learn martial arts.

381
00:40:51.009 --> 00:40:53.944
Get out!

382
00:41:01.520 --> 00:41:04.580
No one learns martial arts here.

383
00:41:04.623 --> 00:41:09.026
This is the most advanced field.

384
00:41:09.060 --> 00:41:10.925
You won't understand it.

385
00:41:10.962 --> 00:41:15.490
I'm willing to start from the bottom.

386
00:41:15.667 --> 00:41:19.763
Dining Room for 35th Chamber

387
00:41:59.978 --> 00:42:03.914
Cross the pond to enter dining hall.

388
00:42:03.949 --> 00:42:05.211
Yes.

389
00:42:11.923 --> 00:42:14.255
Brother. this is the 35th chamber?

390
00:42:14.292 --> 00:42:17.022
Shut up. You starve if you're late.

391
00:42:44.522 --> 00:42:50.427
A pure body is light. steps stable.
stance is firm.

392
00:42:50.462 --> 00:42:54.262
Don't enter the hall if you're dirty.

393
00:44:30.628 --> 00:44:33.153
How dare you enter this dining hall?

394
00:44:33.198 --> 00:44:35.428
Sir. I want to...

395
00:44:35.467 --> 00:44:36.434
Have congee?

396
00:44:42.540 --> 00:44:43.905
Come with me.

397
00:45:01.459 --> 00:45:02.653
Stand on the wood.

398
00:45:04.696 --> 00:45:06.095
Jump.

399
00:45:10.301 --> 00:45:11.598
Turn around!

400
00:45:15.640 --> 00:45:17.005
Eat!

401
00:45:45.336 --> 00:45:47.497
Get up. you're hopeless.

402
00:45:47.539 --> 00:45:50.064
Clean all the pottery and cutlery.

403
00:46:40.592 --> 00:46:44.926
Wall is low. power of Buddha is high.

404
00:46:44.963 --> 00:46:48.194
He's fallen into it.

405
00:46:51.669 --> 00:46:54.069
Don't laugh. he's only a novice.

406
00:46:57.075 --> 00:46:58.872
- Enter the dining hall.
- Yes.

407
00:48:31.903 --> 00:48:33.461
San Ta. you're terrific...

408
00:49:06.904 --> 00:49:10.465
Concentrate. You'll find a way.

409
00:49:10.508 --> 00:49:14.069
Keep practicing day and night. Go!

410
00:49:43.207 --> 00:49:44.902
Stop!

411
00:49:48.312 --> 00:49:52.271
Wood drifts. its buoyancy is limited.

412
00:49:52.316 --> 00:49:58.016
The harder you step. faster it sinks.

413
00:50:00.024 --> 00:50:01.958
- San Ta.
- Yes.

414
00:50:01.993 --> 00:50:04.518
Throw the plate hard into water.

415
00:50:10.435 --> 00:50:13.336
The plate sinks in water.

416
00:50:13.371 --> 00:50:18.172
Just like the wood you stepped upon.

417
00:50:29.020 --> 00:50:33.514
I keep the plate in motion. balanced.

418
00:50:33.558 --> 00:50:39.394
Power takes you forward. firmness
balances the body.

419
00:50:39.430 --> 00:50:41.227
Uniformity of mind.

420
00:50:41.265 --> 00:50:43.859
Focuses power.

421
00:50:43.901 --> 00:50:47.098
You must keep this point in mind.

422
00:51:08.326 --> 00:51:12.319
Power. balance. speed.

423
00:52:14.692 --> 00:52:18.719
Power. balance. speed.
Right.

424
00:52:20.431 --> 00:52:22.092
Sir. I...

425
00:52:22.133 --> 00:52:23.930
Go!

426
00:52:24.702 --> 00:52:28.934
I beg you to teach me. master.

427
00:52:32.009 --> 00:52:35.069
The 34th chamber focuses on training
arms' strength.

428
00:52:35.112 --> 00:52:41.483
Fist. palm. knife. sword. pole. spear.

429
00:52:41.519 --> 00:52:44.955
All depends on the arm's strength. Look...

430
00:52:50.995 --> 00:52:53.020
This is the basic process.

431
00:52:53.064 --> 00:52:56.227
Carry the water up the slope.

432
00:52:56.267 --> 00:53:01.864
Pour it down to keep it flowing.

433
00:53:01.906 --> 00:53:08.971
Remember. arms must be straight.

434
00:53:10.481 --> 00:53:13.939
You should carry water everyday.

435
00:53:13.985 --> 00:53:15.976
To build up arm strength. Go now.

436
00:53:16.020 --> 00:53:17.146
Yes.

437
00:55:12.336 --> 00:55:16.705
I didn't think you'd make it so soon.

438
00:55:22.113 --> 00:55:27.141
Don't help others when they practice.

439
00:55:27.184 --> 00:55:30.153
It'll only ruin them.

440
00:55:30.187 --> 00:55:31.518
Yes.

441
00:55:31.555 --> 00:55:36.322
You've violated our rule. Leave...

442
00:55:36.360 --> 00:55:37.884
Sir...

443
00:55:37.928 --> 00:55:41.489
Go to the 33rd Chamber.

444
00:55:44.668 --> 00:55:46.192
Thank you. sir.

445
00:55:46.370 --> 00:55:49.897
This chamber is comparatively easier.

446
00:55:49.940 --> 00:55:53.376
Whenever you hear me knock the wood.

447
00:55:53.411 --> 00:55:57.939
Strike the gong.

448
00:56:03.387 --> 00:56:06.652
Sir. I'm here to learn kung fu. not...

449
00:56:06.690 --> 00:56:11.889
Don't belittle the bamboo poles.
Ji Wei.

450
00:56:11.929 --> 00:56:12.953
Yes.

451
00:56:20.504 --> 00:56:22.870
The hammer weighs catties.

452
00:56:22.907 --> 00:56:25.637
It is fitted into a 12-ft pole.

453
00:56:25.676 --> 00:56:28.440
With a foot-long pole.
hammer weighs catties.

454
00:56:28.479 --> 00:56:32.973
With the pole extended.
it now weighs catties.

455
00:56:33.017 --> 00:56:36.919
How much can your wrists bear?

456
00:56:36.954 --> 00:56:39.889
I'm willing to try.

457
00:56:57.441 --> 00:57:00.877
Add on more feet.

458
00:57:11.489 --> 00:57:12.922
Ready...

459
00:57:59.403 --> 00:58:00.927
Keep practicing.

460
01:00:33.724 --> 01:00:35.316
My respects to the abbot.

461
01:00:35.359 --> 01:00:40.490
You've left the Wrist Room?

462
01:00:40.531 --> 01:00:45.161
Yes. the overseer said I could leave.

463
01:00:45.202 --> 01:00:49.536
Good. Starting today...

464
01:00:49.573 --> 01:00:51.404
As a reward for your diligence.

465
01:00:51.442 --> 01:00:57.574
You'll be in charge of Sutra Room.

466
01:00:57.614 --> 01:00:59.309
Thank you. abbot.

467
01:01:13.330 --> 01:01:18.529
Brother. San Ta is ambitious.

468
01:01:18.569 --> 01:01:20.901
He's not like our Buddhist brothers.

469
01:01:20.938 --> 01:01:27.468
It's peaceful here in this temple.

470
01:01:27.511 --> 01:01:31.345
But outside it's turbulent.

471
01:01:31.381 --> 01:01:35.374
We may need someone like him.

472
01:01:46.697 --> 01:01:49.393
Please guide me. sir.

473
01:01:55.205 --> 01:01:59.665
Stand between the two burning incense.

474
01:01:59.710 --> 01:02:01.007
Yes.

475
01:02:13.357 --> 01:02:15.655
Anyone practicing martial arts...

476
01:02:15.692 --> 01:02:22.598
Must be sharp-eyed.
Watch the flame.

477
01:02:36.079 --> 01:02:39.139
When the flame oscillates...

478
01:02:39.183 --> 01:02:42.243
Your eyes should follow.

479
01:02:42.286 --> 01:02:46.154
But remember.

480
01:02:46.190 --> 01:02:51.150
Your head must not move.

481
01:02:54.331 --> 01:02:55.958
Start.

482
01:04:04.401 --> 01:04:09.566
Told you not to move your head.
Again.

483
01:04:34.531 --> 01:04:38.558
Right. the target has disappeared.

484
01:04:38.602 --> 01:04:42.368
But still. the eyes shouldn't move.

485
01:04:45.943 --> 01:04:52.143
Eyes be bright. limbs be agile.

486
01:04:52.182 --> 01:04:56.642
This is the way to do it.

487
01:04:56.687 --> 01:04:57.984
Yes.

488
01:05:02.426 --> 01:05:04.485
Turn around.

489
01:05:28.251 --> 01:05:32.984
San Ta. hit the reflecting poles.

490
01:06:26.309 --> 01:06:32.111
You're my most outstanding pupil.

491
01:06:33.717 --> 01:06:35.810
Thank you. sir.

492
01:06:35.986 --> 01:06:38.477
Head Chamber.

493
01:07:11.188 --> 01:07:12.917
Continue

494
01:07:25.969 --> 01:07:27.960
Don't lower your head. Stand up.

495
01:07:29.940 --> 01:07:30.668
Hands on your waist.

496
01:07:30.707 --> 01:07:32.902
Use your head to hit the sand bags.

497
01:07:32.943 --> 01:07:34.672
Then burn incense before the Buddha.

498
01:07:34.711 --> 01:07:36.008
Yes.

499
01:07:54.865 --> 01:07:55.889
Again.

500
01:08:07.377 --> 01:08:08.605
Get up.

501
01:08:08.645 --> 01:08:10.579
Sir. I...

502
01:08:10.614 --> 01:08:14.846
Collapse so soon? Get up now.

503
01:08:14.885 --> 01:08:17.149
Continue. Go on.

504
01:08:52.556 --> 01:08:53.887
Sir.

505
01:08:53.924 --> 01:08:57.382
San Ta.
Were it not for years' hard work.

506
01:08:57.427 --> 01:09:01.488
You might not even take one step
into this alley.

507
01:09:01.531 --> 01:09:06.161
San Ta. head is the most important.

508
01:09:06.203 --> 01:09:09.900
And the last phase in the training.

509
01:09:09.940 --> 01:09:11.999
After going through it.

510
01:09:12.042 --> 01:09:14.909
You can learn fighting and weapons.

511
01:09:21.585 --> 01:09:22.882
Offer the incense.

512
01:09:30.961 --> 01:09:33.987
Use your strength to hit it. Get up!

513
01:09:34.030 --> 01:09:38.990
Come on. get up!

514
01:10:14.037 --> 01:10:15.527
You've set a new record.

515
01:10:16.640 --> 01:10:22.078
You've completed the basic skills...

516
01:10:22.112 --> 01:10:26.014
Of the chambers in months' time.

517
01:10:26.049 --> 01:10:28.279
I can't do it without the teachers.

518
01:10:28.318 --> 01:10:34.723
You can now practise boxing...

519
01:10:34.758 --> 01:10:38.694
Knife. baton and other skills.

520
01:10:38.728 --> 01:10:40.491
Yes.

521
01:10:40.530 --> 01:10:42.964
Justice Officer.

522
01:10:42.999 --> 01:10:47.197
I'll make him head of Dharma House.

523
01:10:52.909 --> 01:10:55.275
San Ta. greet these two abbots.

524
01:10:55.312 --> 01:10:56.973
Yes.

525
01:11:32.048 --> 01:11:33.345
Stop!

526
01:11:49.199 --> 01:11:50.257
Continue!

527
01:12:51.327 --> 01:12:52.351
San Ta!

528
01:12:59.002 --> 01:13:02.995
Leg Chamber.

529
01:13:18.721 --> 01:13:20.018
Sir.

530
01:13:20.056 --> 01:13:25.016
San Ta. not bad. not bad.

531
01:13:29.265 --> 01:13:30.323
Sword Chamber.

532
01:15:27.917 --> 01:15:29.111
Turn around faster.

533
01:16:46.663 --> 01:16:48.494
Good fellow.

534
01:17:06.549 --> 01:17:08.141
San Ta.

535
01:17:21.964 --> 01:17:27.630
San Ta. it's commendable of you.

536
01:17:27.670 --> 01:17:29.865
To master all chambers' kung fu...

537
01:17:29.906 --> 01:17:33.342
In only years.

538
01:17:33.376 --> 01:17:38.973
Now I'll make you deputy overseer of...

539
01:17:39.015 --> 01:17:41.483
Any of the chambers.

540
01:17:41.517 --> 01:17:47.319
Brother. San Ta's post is high enough.

541
01:17:47.356 --> 01:17:49.551
He's been promoted times in years.

542
01:17:49.592 --> 01:17:52.925
With his present skill.

543
01:17:52.962 --> 01:17:56.454
He's qualified to be deputy overseer.

544
01:17:56.499 --> 01:18:00.526
Shaolin arts has existed for years.

545
01:18:00.570 --> 01:18:02.936
We mustn't make a hasty decision.

546
01:18:02.972 --> 01:18:08.308
- What do you think?
- In my opinion...

547
01:18:08.344 --> 01:18:10.642
Let him fight me with any weapon.

548
01:18:10.680 --> 01:18:15.481
If he wins. he can be an overseer.

549
01:18:15.518 --> 01:18:17.952
You heard what he said.

550
01:18:17.987 --> 01:18:22.424
You heard what he said.

551
01:18:22.458 --> 01:18:24.983
What do you think?

552
01:18:25.027 --> 01:18:27.359
I dare not.

553
01:18:27.396 --> 01:18:32.959
It's my idea. If you win...

554
01:18:33.002 --> 01:18:37.098
You can take charge of any chamber.

555
01:18:37.140 --> 01:18:40.906
Excuse me then. sir.

556
01:19:08.471 --> 01:19:09.460
Watch out.

557
01:19:49.412 --> 01:19:51.937
Thank you. sir. I've lost.

558
01:19:56.085 --> 01:19:57.916
You may challenge me any time.

559
01:21:49.165 --> 01:21:52.032
How many times have I tapped you?

560
01:21:52.068 --> 01:21:53.092
17 times.

561
01:21:53.135 --> 01:21:57.162
I could've hurt you with the blade.

562
01:22:03.012 --> 01:22:04.673
You're right.

563
01:22:04.714 --> 01:22:08.650
I'll continue with my practice.

564
01:22:14.190 --> 01:22:18.456
Brother. I think he'll never win.

565
01:22:18.494 --> 01:22:21.122
Not necessarily.

566
01:23:52.421 --> 01:23:54.286
What weapon is San Ta using?

567
01:23:54.323 --> 01:23:58.589
A three-jointed stick invented
by himself.

568
01:24:35.498 --> 01:24:37.591
Good. that blow was not bad.

569
01:24:40.236 --> 01:24:41.225
Go on!

570
01:24:46.876 --> 01:24:48.241
Sir. are you alright?

571
01:24:48.277 --> 01:24:51.576
San Ta. I still have my weapons.

572
01:25:23.712 --> 01:25:25.236
Excuse me.

573
01:25:25.281 --> 01:25:28.876
Abbot.

574
01:25:28.918 --> 01:25:31.944
San Ta can take charge of
any chamber.

575
01:25:31.987 --> 01:25:37.948
San Ta. you can choose
to take charge of...

576
01:25:37.993 --> 01:25:43.954
Any of the chambers except...

577
01:25:43.999 --> 01:25:45.364
The Top Chamber.
Your Buddhism...

578
01:25:45.401 --> 01:25:48.029
Attainment is not advanced enough.

579
01:25:48.070 --> 01:25:49.367
Abbot.

580
01:25:49.405 --> 01:25:51.600
I've not yet made up my mind.

581
01:25:51.640 --> 01:25:55.872
Never mind. I'll give you three days.

582
01:25:55.911 --> 01:25:58.038
Thank you. abbot.

583
01:25:59.014 --> 01:26:02.541
There're only 35 chambers in Shaolin.

584
01:26:02.585 --> 01:26:04.280
There isn't a 36th chamber.

585
01:26:04.320 --> 01:26:09.383
I know. I'd like to create it...

586
01:26:09.425 --> 01:26:11.859
This 36th chamber is...

587
01:26:11.894 --> 01:26:14.226
It's a pity Shaolin martial arts...

588
01:26:14.263 --> 01:26:17.391
Is confined solely to the temple.

589
01:26:17.433 --> 01:26:21.893
It should be taught widely to all.

590
01:26:21.937 --> 01:26:25.998
That's my idea for the new chamber.

591
01:26:26.041 --> 01:26:29.977
To teach martial arts to laymen.

592
01:26:34.550 --> 01:26:37.917
We don't involve in worldly affairs.

593
01:26:37.953 --> 01:26:41.616
Nor do we admit secular pupils.

594
01:26:41.657 --> 01:26:44.285
Forget it.

595
01:26:44.326 --> 01:26:46.453
Abbot. this affects the handing down...

596
01:26:46.495 --> 01:26:47.826
Of Shaolin martial arts to posterity.

597
01:26:47.863 --> 01:26:50.331
Please let me enroll promising youths.

598
01:26:50.366 --> 01:26:52.129
And train them in the 36th chamber.

599
01:26:52.167 --> 01:26:54.635
Nonsense. how dare you talk back?

600
01:27:01.610 --> 01:27:03.134
I don't mean to...

601
01:27:03.178 --> 01:27:06.113
- Shut up!
- I must ask you to reconsider. abbot.

602
01:27:06.148 --> 01:27:07.877
Justice Officer.

603
01:27:07.916 --> 01:27:08.507
Yes.

604
01:27:08.550 --> 01:27:16.082
Our pupil San Ta should be punished.

605
01:27:16.125 --> 01:27:18.286
Yes.

606
01:27:21.930 --> 01:27:24.160
San Ta. you've violated our rule.

607
01:27:24.199 --> 01:27:27.930
You have to collect contributions.

608
01:27:27.970 --> 01:27:30.438
Don't return unless the book is full.

609
01:27:30.472 --> 01:27:36.342
Yes. Abbot. I deserve punishment.

610
01:27:36.378 --> 01:27:41.008
Leave tomorrow morning.

611
01:28:08.944 --> 01:28:10.377
Chiang Tai

612
01:28:26.895 --> 01:28:31.889
You want to pray for Chiang Tai?

613
01:28:31.934 --> 01:28:33.595
They all died.

614
01:28:33.635 --> 01:28:36.536
They were buried in East cemetery.

615
01:28:36.572 --> 01:28:39.564
Go there and pray for them.

616
01:28:50.919 --> 01:28:55.151
Uncle Wei. may you rest in peace.
We will...

617
01:28:55.190 --> 01:28:59.217
complete your mission and restore
the Ming rule.

618
01:28:59.261 --> 01:29:00.285
Hung Hsi-kuan.

619
01:29:00.329 --> 01:29:02.160
Hung Hsi-kuan. I knew you'd be here
to bury your accomplices.

620
01:29:02.197 --> 01:29:03.255
Run!

621
01:29:03.298 --> 01:29:04.287
Go!...

622
01:29:07.436 --> 01:29:09.336
See if you can escape.

623
01:29:09.371 --> 01:29:16.300
Good! I'll kill you one after another.

624
01:29:16.345 --> 01:29:19.872
Go ahead and try.

625
01:30:05.494 --> 01:30:07.985
Tang San-yao. you're so malicious.

626
01:30:08.030 --> 01:30:10.498
Your vice will be punished.

627
01:30:10.532 --> 01:30:12.932
Scram. bloody monk.

628
01:30:12.968 --> 01:30:14.936
Master. please stay out of this.

629
01:30:14.970 --> 01:30:16.528
So you're an accomplice.

630
01:30:23.946 --> 01:30:27.313
Tang San-yao. remember years ago.

631
01:30:27.349 --> 01:30:29.613
You confiscated my school
and my shop.

632
01:30:29.651 --> 01:30:31.016
And kill my whole family?

633
01:30:34.623 --> 01:30:37.956
You're Liu Yu-de. a fugitive! Get him.

634
01:30:43.098 --> 01:30:44.395
Go help your brothers.

635
01:30:44.433 --> 01:30:45.593
Okay!

636
01:32:23.999 --> 01:32:27.457
You're a Buddhist. show mercy.

637
01:32:27.502 --> 01:32:30.665
Even Buddha has to conquer evil.

638
01:32:30.706 --> 01:32:33.174
A monk should not kill.

639
01:32:33.208 --> 01:32:35.540
A monk cannot but I can. I'll do it!

640
01:32:41.683 --> 01:32:45.346
Tang San-yao. you've killed my men.

641
01:32:45.387 --> 01:32:47.446
I'll stab you 1.000 times!

642
01:32:52.160 --> 01:32:55.288
Amitabha Buddha.

643
01:33:04.539 --> 01:33:08.566
Thank God. Today. our martyrs...

644
01:33:08.610 --> 01:33:12.239
Can see you lying dead here.

645
01:33:14.416 --> 01:33:18.580
Master. I want to learn martial arts.

646
01:33:18.620 --> 01:33:20.383
Please accept me as your pupil.

647
01:33:23.592 --> 01:33:28.052
Good. I've come from Shaolin.

648
01:33:28.096 --> 01:33:30.496
To enroll promising youths.

649
01:33:30.532 --> 01:33:34.229
Hsi-kuan. is Tien Ta still in Canton?

650
01:33:34.269 --> 01:33:35.634
Yes.

651
01:33:35.671 --> 01:33:41.337
His hand is stained with Han's blood.

652
01:33:41.376 --> 01:33:47.975
We must eliminate him at all costs.

653
01:33:49.918 --> 01:33:51.852
We'll plan well.

654
01:33:51.887 --> 01:33:54.185
Find a hideout first.

655
01:33:54.222 --> 01:33:55.655
Don't act rashly.

656
01:33:55.691 --> 01:33:59.491
Do you know of other hot-blooded youths?

657
01:33:59.528 --> 01:34:04.158
Yes. Tung Qian-jin is another.

658
01:34:04.232 --> 01:34:09.033
Tung Qian-jin. Commander's orders.

659
01:34:09.071 --> 01:34:10.936
Make a batch of wheels.

660
01:34:19.114 --> 01:34:21.105
Deliver them within one month.

661
01:34:21.149 --> 01:34:23.208
I can't. it'll take one year.

662
01:34:23.251 --> 01:34:26.015
One year? Are you turning me down?

663
01:34:29.725 --> 01:34:35.425
Do you want to join the dead?

664
01:34:35.464 --> 01:34:37.659
Want my help?

665
01:34:39.968 --> 01:34:41.936
I'll teach you to be smarter.

666
01:34:48.577 --> 01:34:49.475
Beat him up!

667
01:35:02.390 --> 01:35:04.881
Are you going to do it or not?

668
01:35:04.926 --> 01:35:06.291
Not over my dead body.

669
01:36:10.959 --> 01:36:13.154
It is better to use the haft.

670
01:36:44.593 --> 01:36:47.824
Help!

671
01:36:47.863 --> 01:36:50.889
Do you still want the wheels made?

672
01:36:50.932 --> 01:36:52.331
No. no!

673
01:36:52.367 --> 01:36:54.028
Damn you!

674
01:36:54.069 --> 01:36:56.003
Good! Good!

675
01:37:01.643 --> 01:37:03.668
Master. Master!

676
01:37:13.488 --> 01:37:18.858
Master... Let me follow you.

677
01:37:18.894 --> 01:37:21.488
Why?

678
01:37:21.529 --> 01:37:24.293
I admire you. Please accept me
as your disciple.

679
01:37:24.332 --> 01:37:25.890
Please take me as your pupil.

680
01:37:25.934 --> 01:37:29.893
Tung Qian-jin. what's wrong with you?

681
01:37:29.938 --> 01:37:32.099
You said you won't submit to anyone.

682
01:37:32.140 --> 01:37:35.974
And will challenge even the Gods?

683
01:37:36.011 --> 01:37:39.469
Why are you kowtowing to a monk now?

684
01:37:40.482 --> 01:37:42.609
What do you know?
He's not a monk.

685
01:37:42.651 --> 01:37:46.087
He's a Bodhisattva.

686
01:37:46.121 --> 01:37:47.611
He only said several words.

687
01:37:47.656 --> 01:37:51.558
And I scared the tartars away.

688
01:37:51.593 --> 01:37:56.587
So he's a living Bodhisattva?

689
01:37:56.631 --> 01:38:01.967
I'm only a monk from Shaolin Temple.

690
01:38:02.003 --> 01:38:06.531
I taught you to avoid direct conflict.

691
01:38:06.574 --> 01:38:11.602
They've learnt kung fu. you haven't.

692
01:38:11.646 --> 01:38:15.309
Using a heavy weapon slows you down.

693
01:38:15.350 --> 01:38:17.181
And puts you at a disadvantage.

694
01:38:17.218 --> 01:38:18.583
Right.

695
01:38:18.620 --> 01:38:23.648
Lu Ah-cai. are you convinced now?

696
01:38:26.127 --> 01:38:27.958
Master. it makes sense.

697
01:38:39.007 --> 01:38:41.271
Lu Ah-cai. can you move?

698
01:38:50.218 --> 01:38:52.584
Lu Ah-cai. don't make hasty moves.

699
01:38:52.620 --> 01:38:54.611
Master. I'm convinced.

700
01:38:54.656 --> 01:38:56.283
Master. I'm convinced.

701
01:39:06.167 --> 01:39:07.361
Are you sure now?

702
01:39:07.402 --> 01:39:10.098
I am. I'm convinced.

703
01:39:10.138 --> 01:39:13.437
Master. please come in for some tea.

704
01:39:45.707 --> 01:39:48.403
Master. I'm really convinced.

705
01:39:57.052 --> 01:39:58.952
How did Tang San-yao die?

706
01:39:58.987 --> 01:40:03.014
You still haven't found out yet?

707
01:40:03.058 --> 01:40:04.616
He was chopped by a knife.

708
01:40:04.659 --> 01:40:10.029
I only want the man who chopped him.

709
01:40:10.065 --> 01:40:12.056
Yes. we're investigating.

710
01:40:12.100 --> 01:40:17.970
Kill all suspects.

711
01:40:18.006 --> 01:40:19.064
Yes.

712
01:40:23.945 --> 01:40:29.178
You must be on the alert.

713
01:40:29.217 --> 01:40:31.481
Yes.

714
01:40:31.519 --> 01:40:34.920
This is General Tien Ta's residence.

715
01:40:34.956 --> 01:40:38.119
He patrols the city every day.

716
01:40:38.159 --> 01:40:40.992
And he must pass through this street.

717
01:40:41.029 --> 01:40:44.362
When he goes to the city gates.

718
01:40:44.399 --> 01:40:48.563
shops on both sides of the street.

719
01:40:48.603 --> 01:40:55.008
Made it difficult for us to get him.

720
01:41:00.715 --> 01:41:03.582
Any households on this street?

721
01:41:03.618 --> 01:41:04.710
Yes.

722
01:41:07.021 --> 01:41:08.352
There is a rice-miller's shop.

723
01:41:08.389 --> 01:41:10.983
Back to back with the General's residence.

724
01:41:11.025 --> 01:41:13.016
Are there many people living there?

725
01:41:13.061 --> 01:41:14.255
There seems to be only one person.

726
01:41:27.242 --> 01:41:28.504
Rice-miller's Shop

727
01:41:39.687 --> 01:41:41.052
Sir.

728
01:41:41.089 --> 01:41:43.182
Amitabha Buddha.

729
01:41:47.495 --> 01:41:48.928
Sir. I...

730
01:41:48.963 --> 01:41:52.160
No one would come for offerings
this late.

731
01:41:52.200 --> 01:41:53.224
What are you doing? Go away...

732
01:42:03.611 --> 01:42:07.342
What do you mean by that?
Go away!

733
01:42:12.453 --> 01:42:13.977
What do you want?

734
01:42:14.022 --> 01:42:16.081
Sir. please excuse me.

735
01:42:16.124 --> 01:42:17.421
What do you want?

736
01:42:17.458 --> 01:42:21.019
May I know your name. sir?

737
01:42:24.032 --> 01:42:25.932
My father died.

738
01:42:25.967 --> 01:42:27.901
Without telling me my name.

739
01:42:27.936 --> 01:42:30.029
So I have no name.

740
01:42:30.071 --> 01:42:33.006
I started milling rice when I was six.

741
01:42:33.041 --> 01:42:36.374
So they call me Miller Six.

742
01:42:36.411 --> 01:42:39.903
I'm San Ta. I'm from Shaolin Temple.

743
01:42:39.948 --> 01:42:45.409
People say that monks from Shaolin...

744
01:42:45.453 --> 01:42:48.354
Are excellent at kung fu. No wonder...

745
01:42:48.389 --> 01:42:50.380
I've practiced for several years.

746
01:42:50.425 --> 01:42:55.260
Having milled rice for many years...

747
01:42:55.296 --> 01:42:57.958
I also have...

748
01:43:01.035 --> 01:43:02.502
a pair of strong feet.

749
01:43:02.537 --> 01:43:07.668
Do you want to try them?

750
01:43:17.685 --> 01:43:19.983
I've drunk a bit too much today.

751
01:43:20.021 --> 01:43:24.685
But your footwork's not bad.

752
01:43:24.726 --> 01:43:29.288
Let's go in for a drink. Let's go!

753
01:43:29.330 --> 01:43:30.888
You can't stay here much longer.

754
01:43:30.932 --> 01:43:32.627
Why not?

755
01:43:32.667 --> 01:43:38.037
Very soon. something big will happen...

756
01:43:38.072 --> 01:43:39.937
in the General's residence.

757
01:43:46.414 --> 01:43:47.938
What is it?

758
01:43:47.982 --> 01:43:52.180
General Tien Ta's going to die here.

759
01:43:52.220 --> 01:43:55.656
How can you say something like that?

760
01:43:55.690 --> 01:43:57.419
Aren't you afraid of being executed?

761
01:43:57.458 --> 01:44:01.155
I beg you to leave here at once. please!

762
01:44:01.195 --> 01:44:02.662
I don't care whether you came from...

763
01:44:02.697 --> 01:44:04.528
Shaolin or Linshao Temple.

764
01:44:04.565 --> 01:44:06.260
Please just leave. I beg you.

765
01:44:06.301 --> 01:44:09.600
The Ching tartars killed so many people.

766
01:44:09.637 --> 01:44:12.333
Don't you want to fight back?

767
01:44:14.075 --> 01:44:17.044
I'm only a rice miller. Even if I did...

768
01:44:17.078 --> 01:44:20.411
What good will it do? I'd rather drink.

769
01:44:20.448 --> 01:44:24.908
People continue to suffer because...

770
01:44:24.952 --> 01:44:28.012
Too many people have that attitude.

771
01:44:28.056 --> 01:44:30.957
You'd put it more plainly.

772
01:44:30.992 --> 01:44:34.359
I want to borrow your place.

773
01:44:34.395 --> 01:44:36.886
No... If you do...

774
01:44:36.931 --> 01:44:38.455
I won't be able to stay here anymore.

775
01:44:38.499 --> 01:44:41.127
Don't worry. I'll take you to Shaolin.

776
01:44:55.683 --> 01:45:02.145
Go away...!
Come here. on your knees...

777
01:45:10.965 --> 01:45:13.593
Lord Cheng. we caught them...

778
01:45:13.634 --> 01:45:14.896
Near the cemetery.

779
01:45:14.936 --> 01:45:17.166
Kill them all!

780
01:45:17.205 --> 01:45:18.467
Yes.

781
01:45:18.506 --> 01:45:20.064
Stop!

782
01:45:22.977 --> 01:45:27.038
Lord Cheng. I killed Tang San-yao.

783
01:45:27.081 --> 01:45:30.016
Not them!

784
01:45:30.051 --> 01:45:31.916
You?

785
01:45:31.953 --> 01:45:37.516
How did you kill him?

786
01:45:45.066 --> 01:45:46.124
With this.

787
01:45:46.167 --> 01:45:47.429
- Take him.
- Yes.

788
01:46:02.450 --> 01:46:03.644
Where did you learn it?

789
01:46:05.553 --> 01:46:06.952
In Shaolin Temple.

790
01:47:52.927 --> 01:47:56.021
- Report to the General! Quick!
- Yes.

791
01:48:38.072 --> 01:48:39.505
Let's go!

792
01:48:51.953 --> 01:48:54.922
Master. we're outnumbered.

793
01:48:54.956 --> 01:48:56.821
Yes. there're so many of them.

794
01:48:56.857 --> 01:48:59.917
Everyday they wake me up early.

795
01:49:03.931 --> 01:49:06.456
Will you please calm down?

796
01:49:06.500 --> 01:49:09.298
No. I can't. I'm Miller Six.

797
01:49:13.674 --> 01:49:15.471
This is flour.

798
01:49:18.546 --> 01:49:24.382
Commanders Tang and Cheng
are famous.

799
01:49:24.418 --> 01:49:26.045
Their failure this time is because...

800
01:49:27.989 --> 01:49:29.889
If more monks were here...

801
01:49:29.924 --> 01:49:33.883
There might be a rebellion in Canton!

802
01:49:33.928 --> 01:49:35.293
Yes...

803
01:49:37.965 --> 01:49:42.061
Tomorrow I'll bring some men
to capture him.

804
01:49:42.103 --> 01:49:46.597
Even if I have to go to Shaolin.

805
01:49:46.641 --> 01:49:48.905
The General's Mansion

806
01:50:00.388 --> 01:50:02.948
Go. go at once... Run!

807
01:51:00.614 --> 01:51:01.945
Give me a sword.

808
01:51:21.535 --> 01:51:25.471
You. a monk. joining the rebels!

809
01:51:30.377 --> 01:51:32.345
A Buddhist has to conquer evil.

810
01:51:32.379 --> 01:51:35.280
How many lives have you taken?

811
01:51:35.316 --> 01:51:40.982
I've killed many. but never a monk.

812
01:54:29.924 --> 01:54:32.051
36th Chamber

813
01:54:46.006 --> 01:54:47.200
Stop!

814
01:55:17.438 --> 01:55:19.906
The sweeping tail of the dancing dragon.

815
01:55:20.000 --> 01:55:23.124
Best watched using Open Subtitles MKV Player
